52.40	Easement	Easement	An easement is a certain right to use the real property of another without possessing it. It is "best typified in the right of way which one landowner, A, may enjoy over the land of another, B."	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/7e/EasementByPriorUseExample.png/220px-EasementByPriorUseExample.png
